<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Marcus Chen — Humanitarian & Speaker</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{--bg:#faf8f5;--fg:#1a1714;--accent:#b44d2d;--accent-light:#e8c4b0;--warm:#f0e6d8;--muted:#7a7068;--card:#fff;--dark:#1a1714;--border:rgba(0,0,0,.08)}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:'Inter',-apple-system,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--fg);overflow-x:hidden;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:1000;padding:0 60px;backdrop-filter:blur(20px);background:rgba(250,248,245,0.92);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border)}
.nav-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;height:72px}
.nav-name{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--fg);text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:-0.3px;cursor:pointer}
.nav-links{display:flex;gap:4px;list-style:none;align-items:center}
.nav-links a{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:13px;font-weight:500;transition:all .3s;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:8px;cursor:pointer}
.nav-links a:hover{color:var(--fg);background:rgba(0,0,0,.04)}
.nav-links a.active{color:var(--accent);background:rgba(180,77,45,.06);font-weight:600}
.nav-cta{background:var(--accent)!important;color:#fff!important;padding:10px 24px!important;border-radius:100px!important;font-weight:600!important;transition:all .3s}
.nav-cta:hover{background:#933d22!important;transform:translateY(-1px)}
.page{display:none;opacity:0;transition:opacity .3s}.page.active{display:block;opacity:1}
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:120px 60px 80px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--bg),var(--warm))}
.hero-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center;width:100%;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.hero-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(180,77,45,.06);color:var(--accent);padding:8px 20px;border-radius:100px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:28px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.hero-badge-dot{width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);animation:pulse 2s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.3}}
.hero h1{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(40px,5vw,68px);line-height:1.08;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:-1.5px;opacity:0;animation:su .8s ease forwards .2s}
.hero h1 span{color:var(--accent)}
.hero-desc{font-size:17px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;max-width:460px;margin-bottom:40px;opacity:0;animation:su .8s ease forwards .4s}
.hero-actions{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;opacity:0;animation:su .8s ease forwards .6s}
.btn-p{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:100px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all .3s;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;cursor:pointer}
.btn-p:hover{background:#933d22;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(180,77,45,.2)}
.btn-s{background:transparent;color:var(--fg);padding:14px 32px;border-radius:100px;font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;border:1.5px solid var(--fg);transition:all .3s;cursor:pointer}
.btn-s:hover{background:var(--fg);color:var(--bg)}
.hero-photo{width:100%;aspect-ratio:4/5;border-radius:20px;overflow:hidden;position:relative;opacity:0;animation:su .8s ease forwards .3s}
.hero-photo img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.hero-photo::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:30%;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(26,23,20,.2),transparent)}
.impact{background:var(--dark);color:#fff;padding:56px 60px}
.impact-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:40px;text-align:center}
.impact-n{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:44px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent-light);letter-spacing:-1px}
.impact-l{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-top:6px}
.section{padding:100px 60px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.s-label{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:4px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);font-weight:600;margin-bottom:16px}
.s-title{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:clamp(28px,3.5vw,42px);line-height:1.15;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:20px;letter-spacing:-0.5px}
.s-desc{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;max-width:560px;margin-bottom:48px}
.mission-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start}
.mission-left p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px}
.m-cards{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:16px}
.m-card{padding:28px;border-radius:14px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);transition:all .4s;box-shadow:0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,.03)}
.m-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.06);border-color:var(--accent-light)}
.m-card-icon{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:10px;background:rgba(180,77,45,.08);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:16px}
.m-card-icon svg{width:22px;height:22px;stroke:var(--accent);fill:none;stroke-width:1.5}
.m-card h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
.m-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
.speaking-section{padding:100px 60px;background:var(--dark);color:#fff}
.speaking-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.speaking-section .s-label{color:var(--accent-light)}
.speaking-section .s-title{margin-bottom:48px;color:#fff}
.ev{display:grid;grid-template-columns:100px 1fr 160px 120px;align-items:center;padding:24px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);transition:all .3s;cursor:pointer;gap:16px}
.ev:first-child{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
.ev:hover{padding-left:12px}
.ev-d{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:15px;color:var(--accent-light);font-weight:600}
.ev-info h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:3px}
.ev-info span{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45)}
.ev-type{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);font-weight:500}
.ev-status{text-align:right;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;padding:4px 14px;border-radius:100px}
.ev-status.open{background:rgba(34,197,94,.1);color:#22c55e}
.ev-status.sold{background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);color:rgba(255,255,255,.3)}
.about-hero{padding:120px 60px 80px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.about-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:400px 1fr;gap:64px;align-items:start}
.about-img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:3/4;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden}
.about-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.about-content h2{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:36px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px;letter-spacing:-0.5px}
.about-content p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:20px}
.about-content p:first-of-type{font-size:19px;color:var(--fg);font-weight:500;line-height:1.6}
.timeline{margin-top:48px}
.timeline h3{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px}
.tl-item{display:grid;grid-template-columns:80px 1fr;gap:20px;padding:20px 0;border-top:1px solid var(--border)}
.tl-year{font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent)}
.tl-text h4{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px}
.tl-text p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5}
.about-values{padding:80px 60px;background:var(--warm)}
.about-values-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.values-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:48px}
.value-card{padding:32px;background:var(--card);border-radius:14px;border:1px solid var(--border)}
.value-card h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.value-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
.media-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:48px}
.media-card{border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--card);transition:all .4s;cursor:pointer}
.media-card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(0,0,0,.06)}
.media-thumb{height:220px;overflow:hidden;position:relative}
.media-thumb img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .5s}
.media-card:hover .media-thumb img{transform:scale(1.05)}
.media-thumb-overlay{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent 50%,rgba(0,0,0,.5));display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:20px}
.media-thumb-type{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;font-weight:600;background:rgba(180,77,45,.85);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:100px}
.media-info{padding:24px}
.media-info h3{font-size:17px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:6px}
.media-info p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:12px}
.media-info .meta{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:500}
.featured-video{margin-top:48px;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#000;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative}
.featured-video img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;opacity:.6}
.play-btn{position:absolute;width:72px;height:72px;border-radius:50%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.95);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .3s}
.play-btn:hover{transform:scale(1.1)}
.play-btn svg{width:24px;height:24px;fill:var(--accent);margin-left:3px}
.impact-hero{padding:120px 60px 60px;background:var(--dark);color:#fff;text-align:center}
.impact-hero .s-label{color:var(--accent-light)}
.impact-hero .s-title{color:#fff;max-width:700px;margin:0 auto 20px}
.impact-hero p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);font-size:17px;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto}
.impact-stats{padding:60px;background:var(--dark)}
.impact-stats-grid{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:32px}
.imp-stat{text-align:center;padding:40px 24px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.02)}
.imp-stat-n{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:48px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent-light);letter-spacing:-1px}
.imp-stat-l{font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);margin-top:8px}
.impact-stories{padding:100px 60px;max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.stories-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:48px}
.story-card{border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border);background:var(--card)}
.story-card-img{height:200px;overflow:hidden}
.story-card-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.story-card-body{padding:24px}
.story-card-body h3{font-size:16px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px}
.story-card-body p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}
.booking{padding:100px 60px;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center}
.booking>p{font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:48px}
.b-cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;text-align:left}
.b-card{padding:36px;border-radius:16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);background:var(--card);transition:all .4s}
.b-card:hover{border-color:var(--accent);transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 16px 48px rgba(180,77,45,.08)}
.b-card-icon{width:48px;height:48px;border-radius:12px;background:rgba(180,77,45,.08);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:20px}
.b-card-icon svg{width:24px;height:24px;stroke:var(--accent);fill:none;stroke-width:1.5}
.b-card h3{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px}
.b-card p{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:24px}
.btn-sm{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:11px 22px;border-radius:100px;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;transition:all .3s}
.btn-sm:hover{background:#933d22}
.contact-form{max-width:560px;margin:48px auto 0;text-align:left}
.form-group{margin-bottom:20px}
.form-group label{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:6px}
.form-group input,.form-group textarea,.form-group select{width:100%;padding:12px 16px;border:1.5px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;font-size:14px;font-family:inherit;background:var(--card);color:var(--fg);transition:border-color .3s;outline:none}
.form-group input:focus,.form-group textarea:focus,.form-group select:focus{border-color:var(--accent)}
.form-group textarea{height:120px;resize:vertical}
.form-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px}
.form-submit{width:100%;padding:14px;border:none;border-radius:100px;background:var(--accent);color:#fff;font-size:15px;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:all .3s;font-family:inherit;margin-top:8px}
.form-submit:hover{background:#933d22}
.testi{padding:80px 60px;background:var(--warm)}
.testi-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.testi .s-title{margin-bottom:48px}
.t-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px}
.t-card{background:var(--card);padding:32px;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.03);border:1px solid var(--border);transition:all .4s}
.t-card:hover{transform:translateY(-3px);box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.06)}
.t-quote{font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:20px;font-style:italic}
.t-author{font-weight:700;font-size:14px}
.t-role{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:2px}
footer{background:var(--dark);color:#fff;padding:72px 60px 36px}
.ft-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto}
.ft-top{display:grid;grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;gap:48px;margin-bottom:48px}
.ft-brand{font-family:'Helvetica Neue',Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:22px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:12px}
.ft-desc{font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);line-height:1.7}
.ft-col h4{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);margin-bottom:16px;font-weight:600}
.ft-col a{display:block;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:10px;transition:color .3s;cursor:pointer}
.ft-col a:hover{color:var(--accent-light)}
.ft-bot{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);padding-top:24px;font-size:12px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);text-align:center}
@keyframes su{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@media(max-width:900px){nav{padding:0 24px}.nav-links a:not(.nav-cta){display:none}.hero{padding:100px 24px 60px}.hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}.impact-inner,.impact-stats-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.impact{padding:40px 24px}.section,.impact-stories,.about-hero,.booking{padding:60px 24px}.mission-grid,.about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.speaking-section{padding:60px 24px}.ev{grid-template-columns:70px 1fr}.ev-type,.ev-status{display:none}.b-cards,.media-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.t-grid,.values-grid,.stories-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.testi,.about-values{padding:60px 24px}footer{padding:48px 24px 24px}.ft-top{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:24px}.form-row{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav><div class="nav-inner">
<a class="nav-name" onclick="showPage('home')">Marcus Chen</a>
<ul class="nav-links">
<li><a onclick="showPage('home')" class="active" data-page="home">Home</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showPage('about')" data-page="about">About</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showPage('speaking')" data-page="speaking">Speaking</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showPage('media')" data-page="media">Media</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showPage('impact')" data-page="impact">Impact</a></li>
<li><a onclick="showPage('contact')" data-page="contact" class="nav-cta">Book Marcus</a></li>
</ul>
</div></nav>

<div id="page-home" class="page active">
<section class="hero"><div class="hero-grid"><div>
<div class="hero-badge"><span class="hero-badge-dot"></span> Protecting 10,000+ Children Monthly</div>
<h1>Fighting for a world where <span>every child is safe</span></h1>
<p class="hero-desc">Entrepreneur, humanitarian, international speaker, and Executive Producer. Founder of the Guardian Initiative — protecting children from trafficking across 23 countries.</p>
<div class="hero-actions"><a onclick="showPage('contact')" class="btn-p">Book Marcus →</a><a onclick="showPage('about')" class="btn-s">Learn More</a></div>
</div>
<div class="hero-photo"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560250097-0b93528c311a?w=600&q=80" alt="Marcus Chen"></div>
</div></section>
<div class="impact"><div class="impact-inner">
<div><div class="impact-n">10K+</div><div class="impact-l">Children Protected Monthly</div></div>
<div><div class="impact-n">23</div><div class="impact-l">Countries Reached</div></div>
<div><div class="impact-n">200+</div><div class="impact-l">Keynotes Delivered</div></div>
<div><div class="impact-n">50M+</div><div class="impact-l">People Reached</div></div>
</div></div>
<section class="section"><div class="mission-grid"><div class="mission-left">
<div class="s-label">The Mission</div>
<h2 class="s-title">Building a global movement to end child trafficking</h2>
<p>Marcus founded the Guardian Initiative after witnessing the devastating reality of child trafficking firsthand. What started as one rescue operation has grown into a global force.</p>
<p>Through partnerships with governments, law enforcement, and local organizations across 23 countries, the Initiative provides rescue operations, safe housing, rehabilitation, and education.</p>
</div><div class="m-cards">
<div class="m-card"><div class="m-card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div><h3>Prevention & Education</h3><p>Community-based programs that identify at-risk children and families before traffickers reach them.</p></div>
<div class="m-card"><div class="m-card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M3 9l9-7 9 7v11a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2z"/><polyline points="9 22 9 12 15 12 15 22"/></svg></div><h3>Rescue & Rehabilitation</h3><p>Direct intervention and long-term care facilities providing housing, therapy, and education.</p></div>
<div class="m-card"><div class="m-card-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg></div><h3>Policy & Advocacy</h3><p>Working with lawmakers to strengthen protections and close legal loopholes.</p></div>
</div></div></section>
<section class="testi"><div class="testi-inner">
<div class="s-label">What People Say</div><h2 class="s-title">Impact Through Words</h2>
<div class="t-grid">
<div class="t-card"><p class="t-quote">"Marcus's keynote was the most powerful we've ever hosted. The entire audience was moved to action."</p><div class="t-author">Sarah Mitchell</div><div class="t-role">Director, Global Impact Summit</div></div>
<div class="t-card"><p class="t-quote">"His ability to combine data-driven storytelling with raw emotion is unmatched. Transformative."</p><div class="t-author">Dr. James Park</div><div class="t-role">Dean, Kennedy School</div></div>
<div class="t-card"><p class="t-quote">"Our listeners rated this the #1 episode of the year. Marcus's story is one everyone needs to hear."</p><div class="t-author">Lisa Torres</div><div class="t-role">Host, The Change Makers</div></div>
</div></div></section>
</div>

<div id="page-about" class="page">
<div class="about-hero"><div class="about-grid">
<div class="about-img"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1475721027785-f74eccf877e2?w=600&q=80" alt="Marcus Chen Speaking"></div>
<div class="about-content">
<div class="s-label">About Marcus</div>
<h2>A life dedicated to protecting the vulnerable</h2>
<p>Marcus Chen is an entrepreneur, humanitarian, and international speaker whose work has reached over 50 million people worldwide.</p>
<p>As the founder of the Guardian Initiative, Marcus has built an organization that protects over 10,000 children monthly from trafficking across 23 countries. His approach combines grassroots intervention with systemic policy change.</p>
<p>Before founding the Guardian Initiative, Marcus spent a decade in business building ventures across Asia and Europe. A pivotal encounter during a trip to Southeast Asia changed his trajectory forever.</p>
<p>Marcus is also an Executive Producer of the award-winning documentary series "Unseen," which has been instrumental in raising global awareness about trafficking.</p>
<div class="timeline"><h3>Journey</h3>
<div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-year">2024</div><div class="tl-text"><h4>UN Advisory Role</h4><p>Appointed advisor on child protection policy to the United Nations</p></div></div>
<div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-year">2022</div><div class="tl-text"><h4>"Unseen" Documentary</h4><p>Executive produced award-winning documentary reaching 20M+ viewers</p></div></div>
<div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-year">2019</div><div class="tl-text"><h4>23 Countries Reached</h4><p>Guardian Initiative expanded operations across 4 continents</p></div></div>
<div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-year">2016</div><div class="tl-text"><h4>Guardian Initiative Founded</h4><p>Launched with first rescue operation in Southeast Asia</p></div></div>
<div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-year">2014</div><div class="tl-text"><h4>The Turning Point</h4><p>Encountered trafficking firsthand during business trip to Cambodia</p></div></div>
