<div class="about-values"><div class="about-values-inner">
<div class="s-label">Core Values</div><h2 class="s-title">What drives the work</h2>
<div class="values-grid">
<div class="value-card"><h3>Action Over Words</h3><p>Every strategy must lead to tangible, measurable impact. The urgency of the crisis demands it.</p></div>
<div class="value-card"><h3>Survivor-Centered</h3><p>Survivors are at the heart of every decision — their dignity, agency, and recovery come first.</p></div>
<div class="value-card"><h3>Systemic Change</h3><p>Individual rescue is essential, but lasting impact requires changing the systems that enable exploitation.</p></div>
</div></div></div>
</div>

